  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do you find \"coming soon\" projects on Kickstarter and Indiegogo?",
  "response": "To find \"coming soon\" projects on Kickstarter and Indiegogo, you can follow these steps:\n\nFor Kickstarter:\n\n1. Visit the Kickstarter website at www.kickstarter.com.\n2. On the homepage, click on the \"Discover\" tab in the top navigation menu.\n3. In the left sidebar, you'll see a list of categories. Scroll down and click on \"Coming Soon\" under the \"Discover\" section.\n4. You'll be taken to a page that displays projects that are scheduled to launch soon. You can browse through these projects and explore the ones that interest you.\n\nFor Indiegogo:\n\n1. Visit the Indiegogo website at www.indiegogo.com.\n2. On the homepage, hover over the \"Explore\" tab in the top navigation menu and click on \"Coming Soon\" from the dropdown menu.\n3. You'll be directed to a page showcasing projects that are set to launch soon on the platform. Browse through the listings and click on any project that catches your attention to learn more about it.\n\nOn both platforms, you can use the search and filter options to narrow down the \"coming soon\" projects based on your interests, categories, or location. Additionally, you can sign up for notifications on projects you're interested in, so you'll be alerted when they officially launch and are ready for backing.",
